Core Shared Modules
-------------------
- CartContext: provides cartItems, addToCart, removeFromCart, updateQuantity, clearCart, getCartTotal, getCartCount.
- useCart consumers: Header, ProductCard, ProductDetail, Cart, Checkout.
- products data consumers: Header, Home, Shop, ProductDetail.

